{
  "stem": "20711.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, our automobile-- which was the only car in the whole town-- my father transferred the title to my grandmother's name.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My Catholic grandmother's name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also some of our vine-- vineyard were transferred to some of my aunts' name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never questioned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was a wise businessman, and I just assumed he knew what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he never told us why he's doing it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just later I was thinking on how wise he was and how ahead he was going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only incident-- I can barely recall it, but I do remember somebody-- a local young man in his early 20s or late teens broke a window in a Jewish home and everybody was [? appalled ?] by that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But even that young man, the only accuse-- [LAUGHS] only excuse I have for him, he was no longer a lo-- a local person.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a young 15, 16 year old, he left town, and he started to work in a factory in one of the cities-- I don't where-- where he got probably a lot of propaganda and lot of co-worker who might have been anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when he came home visit his family, he just acted like what he learned in the city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But everybody, including the town, condemned him for his action.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that was the only thing I can recall it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The only other incident which was very historical in my life, and it was before I went to the boarding school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Exactly when the war broke out, which was in September 1939, we received an awful-- Hungary received an awful lot of Polish refugees.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Most of them were running away from the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
